{"tid":1991968,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【思捷玩完】ESPRIT亞洲56店將全線結業 四大經典逐樣數","createTime":"2020-04-28T00:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T04:22:33.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d42230fb1e142fc479dde00a052f481aaa00e3e2","tid":1991968,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:29:20.000Z","msg":"思捷經典趣事一覽：<br />\n<br />\n曾打入美容界：<br />\n<br />\n九十年代的ESPRIT不但做男、女裝、童裝，亦有化粧和美容護膚品牌Red Earth和髮型屋Salon ESPRIT。99年面世的Salon ESPRIT更是話題之作，因為找來當時人氣髮型師Kim Robinson坐陣，全盛時全港有逾10家分店，名媛明星至愛，惟2012年在香港全線結業。<br />\n明星效應：<br />\n<br />\n邢李㷧94年迎娶林青霞後，大美人都穿ESPRIT，更不時被拍下到ESPRIT「掃貨」。當年旺角惠豐中心的ESPRIT Megastore開幕，由林青霞、張國榮及梅艷芳三人剪綵。影星舒淇和趙薇等曾是Red Earth的代言人。<br />\n三SPRIT事件：<br />\n<br />\n軟硬天師林海峰和葛民輝，入行前曾一齊在ESPRIT興發街店擔任櫥窗設計，後來在《車欠石更》專輯中作品《川保久齡大戰山本耀司》亦唱到「永遠懷念興發街嗰間ESPRIT」；主持電台節目《老人院時間》時，當中《整蠱電話》環節曾故意將ESPRIT讀成「三SPRIT」，因品牌中的E字像中文字「三」。<br />\n劉天蘭擔任「形象聖手」：<br />\n<br />\nESPRIT於1987年增設了一個叫Image Director（形象總監）的職務，並由「形象聖手」劉天蘭擔任，例如各間分店內要播放甚麼音樂，並請來Andrew Bull為時裝店打造背景音樂，而售貨員的服飾設計、制服配襯、分店內貨品的排列擺設以至是擺放甚麼氣味的香薰，都由她策劃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDdPAjn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsDdPAjn.jpg&h=903a8605&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47e13d751c24dc953800721f58bcdd3bc323f4e6","tid":1991968,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:30:10.000Z","msg":"有無人知Kim Robinson去咗邊？"},{"pid":"562fa8a0b2ef101acd2263c5daec89883ecd8116","tid":1991968,"uid":244152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47e13d751c24dc953800721f58bcdd3bc323f4e6","tid":1991968,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:30:10.000Z","msg":"有無人知Kim Robinson去咗邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:31:41.000Z","msg":"中環開髮廊"},{"pid":"d3ebf9ac6a6a4570bb9908cfa2e5d27df517940c","tid":1991968,"uid":254813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"47e13d751c24dc953800721f58bcdd3bc323f4e6","tid":1991968,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:30:10.000Z","msg":"有無人知Kim Robinson去咗邊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:36:11.000Z","msg":"做左cctvb合約藝人"},{"pid":"ece5e99e0104a0d66139f48d874ff3d90d613eb9","tid":1991968,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:39:19.000Z","msg":"細個行又一城見到間Salon Esprit好高級，阿媽話好很貴"},{"pid":"cd4d9b213d18795a38363e56e16437ec3bbd7d0e","tid":1991968,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:40:09.000Z","msg":"八 、九十年代去esprit = 型＋潮<br />\n<br />\n利申：未幫襯過"},{"pid":"5cc8322300a989167604caa63d531230379e4791","tid":1991968,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:41:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03d5f37a58d3cac467c0f59b684edba456584808","tid":1991968,"uid":77092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:41:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"153e7051a4f851b0ec92a50a2e0b03e6d1a52883","tid":1991968,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ece5e99e0104a0d66139f48d874ff3d90d613eb9","tid":1991968,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:39:19.000Z","msg":"細個行又一城見到間Salon Esprit好高級，阿媽話好很貴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:43:25.000Z","msg":"以前去利舞台muji嗰陣一定會望到間salon，覺得入面啲人好有錢"},{"pid":"79ff06d3b89cbb7bab7560ba4708b24f86b7960f","tid":1991968,"uid":32816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T00:46:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w21qAHw0Ihw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw21qAHw0Ihw&d=WEVEcTK9c1gYxUU7eN%2BS4f7iMF%2BZ1QNuv%2BvReNsMrP0%3D&h=d7d168f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w21qAHw0Ihw</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af257dfe959e04d4d036c50a24e935e1add7816a","tid":1991968,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi